.github/workflows/android-release-ci.yml

```yaml
name: Android Release CI

on:
  push:
    branches: [ main, master ]
  workflow_dispatch:

jobs:
  build-release:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - name: Checkout repository
        uses: actions/checkout@v4

      - name: Setup JDK 17
        uses: actions/setup-java@v4
        with:
          distribution: temurin
          java-version: '17'

      - name: Set up Android SDK
        uses: android-actions/setup-android@v2
        with:
          sdk-version: 34

      - name: Decode release keystore
        env:
          ANDROID_KEYSTORE_B64: ${{ secrets.ANDROID_KEYSTORE_B64 }}
        run: |
          echo "$ANDROID_KEYSTORE_B64" | base64 --decode > release-keystore.jks

      - name: Build release APK
        env:
          ANDROID_KEYSTORE_PASSWORD: ${{ secrets.ANDROID_KEYSTORE_PASSWORD }}
          ANDROID_KEY_ALIAS: ${{ secrets.ANDROID_KEY_ALIAS }}
          ANDROID_KEY_PASSWORD: ${{ secrets.ANDROID_KEY_PASSWORD }}
        run: |
          ./gradlew assembleRelease \
            -PKEYSTORE_PASSWORD=$ANDROID_KEYSTORE_PASSWORD \
            -PKEY_ALIAS=$ANDROID_KEY_ALIAS \
            -PKEY_PASSWORD=$ANDROID_KEY_PASSWORD --stacktrace

      - name: Upload signed APK artifact
        uses: actions/upload-artifact@v4
        with:
          name: app-release-apk
          path: app/build/outputs/apk/release/app-release.apk
```

说明：
- 在 GitHub 仓库 Secrets 中设置：
  - `ANDROID_KEYSTORE_B64`：keystore Base64 内容
  - `ANDROID_KEYSTORE_PASSWORD`：keystore 密码
  - `ANDROID_KEY_ALIAS`：alias 名称
  - `ANDROID_KEY_PASSWORD`：key 密码
- push 或手动触发 workflow 后，成功构建的 release APK 会作为 artifact 上传，可以下载。
